### AppHost 直连模式 TenantAppInstances V2 API 验证
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5002
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!
@appId = 1

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 获取 CSRF Token
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###

### 实例列表（用于确认 appId）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 设置页：查询实例详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{appId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 组织管理：查询角色列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{appId}}/roles?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&keyword=&sortBy=&sortDesc=false
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 组织管理：查询部门列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{appId}}/departments?pageIndex=1&pageSize=20&keyword=&sortBy=&sortDesc=false
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 组织管理：查询部门全量
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{appId}}/departments/all
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 组织管理：查询职位列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{appId}}/positions?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&keyword=&sortBy=&sortDesc=false
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 组织管理：查询组织工作区
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{appId}}/organization/workspace?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&keyword=
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 设置页：更新实例
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{appId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Direct 模式联调应用",
  "description": "用于验证 AppHost v2 组织与设置链路",
  "category": "DEV",
  "icon": "*"
}

### 设置页：发布实例
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{appId}}/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 设置页：启动实例
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{appId}}/start
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 设置页：停止实例
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{appId}}/stop
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 设置页：重启实例
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/tenant-app-instances/{{appId}}/restart
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

